{
  "page": "Raynard Ruskyn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ruskyn\" title=\"House Ruskyn\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Raynard Ruskyn</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/50px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/75px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/100px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ruskyn\" title=\"House Ruskyn\">House Ruskyn</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Raynard Ruskyn</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ruskyn\" title=\"House Ruskyn\">House Ruskyn</a>. He became <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynard_Ruskyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>By <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a>, Ser Raynard was a sworn brother of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>. King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a> defied an attempted coup against the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogare\" title=\"House Rogare\">Rogare family</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Thaddeus_Rowan\" title=\"Thaddeus Rowan\">Thaddeus Rowan</a>, beginning a <a href=\"/index.php/Secret_siege\" title=\"Secret siege\">secret siege</a>. Raynard was imprisoned in <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor%27s_Holdfast\" title=\"Maegor&#39;s Holdfast\">Maegor's Holdfast</a> after being overwhelmed and wounded by the <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> guards of <a href=\"/index.php/Larra_Rogare\" title=\"Larra Rogare\">Larra Rogare</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the aftermath of the coup, Raynard was released from captivity, and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a>, was mortally wounded when he confronted Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Mervyn_Flowers\" title=\"Mervyn Flowers\">Mervyn Flowers</a>, a fellow Kingsguard and one of the conspirators. At some point, Marston was heard to say to Raynard about Mervyn, \"We are the both of us <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastards</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Sworn_Brother\" title=\"Sworn Brother\">Sworn Brothers</a> besides\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Several royal offices were filled at the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Council_of_136_AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Great Council of 136 AC\">Great Council of 136 AC</a>, including the promotion of Ser Raynard to Lord Commander, left vacant by Marston's death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Raynard_Ruskyn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Lysene Spring and the End of Regency.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">