"2\"><div>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robin_Massey\" title=\"Robin Massey\">Robin Massey</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Darklyn\" title=\"Robert Darklyn\">Robert Darklyn</a> were named respectively as member and Lord Commander of the Kingsguard by Aegon III,<br />but the appointment was later set aside by <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">Lord Regent</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Unwin_Peake\" title=\"Unwin Peake\">Unwin Peake</a>.\n</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Lords_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Template:Lords Commander of the Kingsguard\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Lords_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Lords Commander of the Kingsguard (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Lords_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lords Commander of the Kingsguard</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Lords Commander to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon_(son_of_Daemon)\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon (son of Daemon)\">Corlys Velaryon</a> (10-?)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addison_Hill\" title=\"Addison Hill\">Addison Hill</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gyles_Morrigen\" title=\"Gyles Morrigen\">Gyles Morrigen</a> (48-?)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ryam_Redwyne\" title=\"Ryam Redwyne\">Ryam Redwyne</a> (?-105)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harrold_Westerling\" title=\"Harrold Westerling\">Harrold Westerling</a> (?-112)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Criston_Cole\" title=\"Criston Cole\">Criston Cole</a> (112-130)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Willis_Fell\" title=\"Willis Fell\">Willis Fell</a> (131-133)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marston_Waters\" title=\"Marston Waters\">Marston Waters</a> (133-135)<sup>*</sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Raynard Ruskyn</a> (136-?)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Connington\" title=\"Alyn Connington\">Alyn Connington</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Demon_of_Darry\" title=\"Demon of Darry\">Demon of Darry</a></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Flowers\" title=\"Robert Flowers\">Robert Flowers</a></li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_II)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Viserys II)\">Aemon Targaryen</a> (?-178/183)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan t